name: Army of Hardcore - Thank You Party
description:
I heard the promoter say, "cameraman get up here and do your thing!", so I weaved through the crowd and captured this Group Photo moment. Getting back into the groove of event photography feels really good. 

See you at the next show. 

Date: 1/22/22
Music Genre: Hardcore Drum and Bass
Venue: Catch One in Los Angeles California.
Camera: Sony A7IV
Lens: Tamron 17-28mm
Photographer: Sebuh Honarchian
